  "body": "- [x] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\nCannot `npm install @truffle/hdwallet-provider` on `macOS Catalina 10.15`\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n1. setup: macOS Catalina 10.15\r\n2. run `npm install @truffle/hdwallet-provider`\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nThe `@truffle/hdwallet-provider` package should be installed in `node_modules` with all its dependencies\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\nThe error messages  `No receipt for ... found at '/'` , and `gyp: No Xcode or CLT versione detected!` \r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36712489/67287852-25764080-f4dc-11e9-8413-013252fa3642.png)\r\n\r\nBut I do have Xcode CLT installed (see below):\r\n\r\n![image (1)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36712489/67287983-68d0af00-f4dc-11e9-8e30-f533f2bdc172.png)\r\n\r\nI assume this error is due to the fact that`macOS Catalina `changed quite a bit regarding the `/ ` directory - it is `read-only` now\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: macOS Catalina 10.15\r\n* Ethereum client: \r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): 5.0.22 \r\n* node version (`node --version`): 10.16.3\r\n* npm version (`npm --version`):  6.11.3\r\n",
