    "body": "I was able to resolve the issue by deleting my `/Library/Developer/CommandLineTools` directory and reinstalling via `xcode-select --install` -- I followed this way of reinstalling the xcode commandlinetools because I never installed Xcode the app itself - I only ever installed the command line tools. The approach for reinstalling them might differ for people that installed them via Xcode the app itself.",
